title: Recipe Time estimator
description: Using recipe data to build a model that can estimate recipe time using the ingredients and the number steps of the recipe. Model is implemented using a decision tree model.

title: Larvae Image Classifer
description: Building an AI-image classifier to distinguish between generalists and human specialists morphologically and identify areas on the larvae that are different.

title: Deceptive Data Visualization
description: Making multiple data visualization using the same dataset to provide evidence that support opposing arguments. This project showcases how data visualize can be exploited to draw favorable conclusions, and urges against unethical data visualization
